WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.931
Email is your written record. Customers save it, forward it, print it.

00:00:03.981 --> 00:00:08.245
Five details make the difference. A clear subject line that names the vehicle

00:00:08.295 --> 00:00:12.558
and the service. A real greeting with their name — not Hi there.

00:00:12.608 --> 00:00:16.871
Short paragraphs or bullets, never a wall of text. Proofread once before you

00:00:16.921 --> 00:00:21.184
send, because autocorrect mistakes live forever in an inbox. And close with the

00:00:21.234 --> 00:00:25.497
actual next step and your contact information. One last trick — read the

00:00:25.547 --> 00:00:29.810
email aloud before you send. Tone you can hear is tone you can

00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:30.260
fix.
